@node Oprogramu "Introduction"

    @{B}BlueInstall@{UB} is a little tool especially for sending a disks with archives,
pictures or texts to Your friend. @{I}Check it out! @{UI}

@endnode

@node Shareware "Shareware"
    This program is shareware.

    The registration fee is @{FG SHINE}10 USD/DM@{FG text} or equivalent in other currency.
Please, send only banknotes and @{B}NO COINS!@{UB}

    If You Are a registered user of other product of @{I}Blue Legend @{UI}then the registration
fee is @{FG SHINE}5 USD/DM@{FG text}.

    If You want to register, please print and fillout the Registation form and send
Registration form + one disk + Registration fee to address of @{"author" link kontakt}.

    You will Get the disk back with the latest version of @{"BlueInstall" link Oprogramu}.

    There are no diferencies between registered and unregistered version, but
if You have some problems with the registered version, the @{"author" link kontakt} and
@{I}Blue Legend @{UI}will help you.

